Package: ESPENAPI
Type: Package
Title: A Tool to Access Data from the ESPEN Portal API
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Olatunji Johnson [cre, aut] (<https://orcid.org/0000-0002-4080-0999>)
Maintainer: Olatunji Johnson <olatunjijohnson21111@gmail.com>
Description: Allows users to access Neglected Tropical Diseases (NTDs) data from
    the ESPEN portal API. Users provide parameters as specified in
    <https://admin.espen.afro.who.int/docs/api/data> and the function returns a 
    dataframe or JSON strings.
Imports: jsonlite, httr
License: GPL
Encoding: UTF-8
